<HEADLINE> Albright Meets With Montenegro Head  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   BERLIN (AP) -- Secretary of State Madeleine Albright met Saturday
with President Milo Djukanovic of Montenegro, signaling U.S.
support for the smaller of the two republics that make up
Yugoslavia.
</P>
<P>
   Albright offered her sympathy for the slaying of Goran Zugic,
the national security adviser in the independence-minded republic,
a senior U.S. official said.
